        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>In order to improve the performance of the motorized mirrors on the HPV family of trucks, a new
                    mirror actuator has been made available. This new actuator can be installed on any vintage HPV truck
                    that is equipped with motorized mirrors. This TSI contains complete instructions on installing the
                    new actuator on trucks built prior to 08/28/06.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
